{"tid":1068002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人赴中國管制細則？蘇貞昌：唱中國國歌都應禁止","createTime":"2019-03-19T02:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T07:27:56.000Z","uid":144372,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93c3196fd08b679ccdea98fdfb65bfe4ee9b8537","tid":1068002,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/退將赴中管制細則-蘇貞昌-致敬-唱中國國歌都應禁止-102306756.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%80%80%E5%B0%87%E8%B5%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E7%B4%B0%E5%89%87-%E8%98%87%E8%B2%9E%E6%98%8C-%E8%87%B4%E6%95%AC-%E5%94%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E9%83%BD%E6%87%89%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2-102306756.html&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=64ee489d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/退將赴中管制細則-蘇貞昌-致敬-唱中國國歌都應禁止-102306756.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今（26）日立法院召開第7會期第2次會議，陸委會擬於此會期裡修訂「兩岸人民關係條例」，加強對退休將領和政務官赴中國參訪的條件管制。然而今（26）日行政院長蘇貞昌在總質詢時被國民黨立委問及，所謂「參與政治性活動的定義到底是什麼」時，蘇貞昌回應，「對岸領導人不放棄武力犯台，但你卻去唱國歌，向他致敬，是不對的，所謂的管制指的是這個」。"},{"pid":"17af10f4c201ba0d47b51c3402c42b807d7c922d","tid":1068002,"uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"第時佢哋去香港<br />\n<br />\n唱又犯法唔唱又犯法"},{"pid":"99bea1dc4d5779dac167b066755fbd346ca5c3c1","tid":1068002,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"國軍係時候反攻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a80cbeb85146cc8b3be508fc342fe5e63656cc2","tid":1068002,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"係香港唱算唔算？"},{"pid":"3f99d11241b401783bfc891a5b22efb32eb6dec3","tid":1068002,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"國台辦d人唔知會唔會唱匪歌呢？<br />\n踢曬佢地走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}